                <span class="absolute bottom-[20%] right-[0%] bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-300 shadow-2xl animate-[spin_12s_linear_infinite] flex items-center gap-1.5">
